title: Emerica Presents: Provost x Mouse Limited Collab
description:
Emerica’s teamed up with Collin Provost’s long time homie ,Mouse, to customize his signature Cruiser Slip-on's. 

Mouse individually painted each shoe, with a limited quantity of only 666 available.

Out now with a narrow supply only at #HigherQuality shops.
